{
  "text": "The following four human NB cell lines were used and evaluated in this study. They are NB-19 [CITATION_1] , KP-N-SIFA [CITATION_2] , SK-N-DZ [CITATION_3] and LAN-1 [CITATION_4] , which were studied in our previous papers [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] . All these 4 cell lines were cultured in RPMI1640 (R8758, Sigma) medium supplemented with 10 % fetal bovine serum (FBS) (GIBCO). Cells were incubated in a humidified atmosphere at 37 °C with 5 % CO 2 .",
  "correct_citation": {
